@startuml
title Manage Appointment
actor Resepsionis
participant Sistem
participant Database

Resepsionis -> Sistem : Ubah atau batalkan appointment
Sistem -> Database : Update data appointment
Database --> Sistem : Status update

alt Berhasil
    Sistem --> Resepsionis : Konfirmasi perubahan
else Gagal
    Sistem --> Resepsionis : Gagal memproses
end
@enduml